Synergy-Framework is Hadoop Map/Reduce framework, integrated with Surus ORM and Synergy-Scheduler
Framework features:

* Process context specifying mapper, reducer, input, output by process name
* Input/Output support both files and HBase tables
* Surus ORM support for work with HBase tables
* REST interface workpiece
* Socket-level tunnels for high-throughout-put of the data into the HBase from third-party clients (i.e. Python, remote Java, etc)
* XML-driven HBase table schema creation and deletion

Synergy-Scheduler project:
https://github.com/mushkevych/scheduler

HBase Surus ORM:
https://github.com/mushkevych/surus